snippet.title: 🔴 Livestream: Teal Tuesday Team Takeover
snippet.description:
Dallas is away, and The Chosen Team is taking over for Teal Tuesday and the BIGGEST sale of the year! https://thechosengifts.com/
Join us today for an 8 hour livestream starting at 4p CT including:
• The release of one of the items you request most
• Giveaways every 10 minutes
• A new sticker, free with every order (while supplies last)
• Actor shenanigans
• A chance to meet the team behind the scenes at The Chosen
• FREE Shipping
• And a chance to win a prize pack that will Blow Your Mind if you last all 8 hours!
